        <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PK = Primary Key (bold + underline)&lt;br&gt;FK = Foreign Key (italic)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Crow&#39;s Foot:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;⟨‖ = exactly one (mandatory)&lt;br&gt;○&amp;lt; = zero or many&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Relationships:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• One User → Many Bookings (1:N)&lt;br&gt;• Many Bookings → One Match (N:1)&lt;br&gt;• Each Booking row = exactly one User + one Match (logical 1:1 per reserved seat)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f5f5f5;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;spacing=10;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
